Труды Кубанского государственного аграрного университета 2(17), 2009. – С. 156-161. 



















Efficiency of biological and chemical means of protection of winter wheat from sheet diseaseS in THE GRAIN-GRASS INTERTILLAGE crop rotation.

          This article presents results of long-term researches of economic effect of the biological and chemical means of plant protection on various sorts of winter wheat in conditions of the long stationary experience of Kuban State Agrarian University. There were made conclusions that the choice of protection system depends upon specific structure of originators of diseases, conditions of their population. The impact of protection factor on productivity of winter wheat was determined using method of mathematical analysis.

Economic effect, means of plant protection, fungicides, biological plant protection, chemical plant protection, population, factor, winter wheat, productivity.



 protection, population, factor, winter wheat, productivity.



